<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN349-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. maturai marutaṉiḷanāyakaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div> 
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN349">
<l>nutivēl koṇṭu nutalviyar tuṭaiyāk</l>
<l>kaṭiya kūṟum vēntē tantaiyu</l>
<l>neṭiya vallatu paṇintumoḻi yalaṉē</l>
<l>yiḵtivar paṭiva māyiṉ vaiyeyiṟ</l>
<l>ṟarimatar maḻaikka ṇammā varivai</l>
<l>marampaṭu ciṟutīp pōla</l>
<l>vaṇaṅkā yiṉaṭāṉ piṟanta vūrkkē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wiping sweat off [his] forehead with [his] pointed spear</l>
<l>the king talks harshly. And [her] father,</l>
<l>besides [talking] at length does not speak humbly.</l>
<l>If this [is] their penance, that dark young woman</l>
<l>with sharp teeth [and] read-streaked beautiful rain eyes,</l>
<l>like a small fire befalling a tree,</l>
<l>has become a plague to the village she was born in.  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
